name: Prank Call
shortDescription: Have you ever needed to call one of your friends on restricted number or Private Number? This app eliminates the hassle of writing down the number on a paper then typing it into your phone.  No more changing the contacts number in your phone - this app does all the work for you!  Just choose a contact from your phone and it changes it to a restricted number for you! Nothing is saved - its just for this call! FEATURES: *Makes restricted number calling EASY! *Save Contacts into the restricted number Favorites *Generate random number *Great for Drunk Dials! What are you waiting for?  Start Prank calling your friends EASILY with Prank Calls!
author: Ryan Bertrand
